CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1959, pg. A3 reads: "Tops All Agents - William Chandler, second from left, receives first-prize trophy from E.A. Palm, left, and J.D. Lewis, right, is shown presenting the Staff Manager trophy to Miss Maude Y. Hawkins, second from right.  The awards were given for top production of agents during the observance of National Insurance Week, which opened May 11, with North Carolina Mutual Life Insurance Company agents setting the pace. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: North Carolina Mutual Life Insurance Company winning agents, from left: William Chandler, receiving first-place trophy from E.A. Palm, right, and Maude Y. Hawkins, receiving Staff Manager trophy from J.D. Lewis, posed in front of toteboard in interior
